content:
During the dismantling of the rubble of a five-story residential building destroyed by a russian strike, rescuers unblocked the second body of a dead person.

About thisinformsState Emergency Service of Ukraine.

“During the analysis of the blockage of a 5-storey dwelling house, the SES's employees were thawed by the body of the second dead person. There are currently 2 dead and 8 injured people as a result of a nightly Russian attack in the city, ”the message reads.

The SESA added that the work on parsing the rubble continues.

As reported by the Armyinform, on the site of the Russian blow in Sumyfoundthe body of the dead man.
